{
  "stem": "3475.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then after a while, the thing-- after a while, when they drove us into the railroad cars, then I lost, lost sight of her, you know, because you had no choice where you went-- wherever they pushed you.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and the railroad cars, they just had little windows on top, barred with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were maybe two windows on top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they packed the whole car with people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was unbelievably hot and stuffy there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't hardly breathe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "God, [SIGHS] hundreds of people they shoved in a wagon, you know, cattle-- like cattle cars, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were not open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It would be good if they were open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember, when we took off, the only nice thing about it-- you could hear the railroad whistles, you know, you know, this-- the-- which was the only pleasant thing you could hear, is the railroad whistle.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, during the night, I lost my-- I don't know whether it was at night or in the daytime-- I think we went like two days and two nights.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I lost consciousness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what I remember, to this day-- the dream that I had, like, that I was laying on a field of green grass, with a river or a brook.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To this day, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I guess I was dreaming of something that I would like to happen to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then, I-- when, when-- finally, when I woke up-- I must have passed out, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I woke up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they opened the doors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they started, los, los, los, pulling everybody out, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
